net.bytebuddy.utility

Enum PropertyDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PropertyDispatcher>
      • net.bytebuddy.utility.PropertyDispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<PropertyDispatcher>

    public enum PropertyDispatcher
extends Enum<PropertyDispatcher>
    A dispatcher for invoking Object.toString() and Object.hashCode() methods that are sensitive to array values which need redirection to different specialized methods defined by Arrays.
